page.title: 13Dores/Abriachan_Wildlife
page.content: The Highlands of Scotland have lots of animals such as {Deer,Foxes,Rabbits} etc. Deer Stalking and Pheasant Shooting or Grouse Shooting are popular sports for people who can afford them.The deer are 3 different species{Red,Sikka}and{Roe.}Red deer tend to stay on the high ground and in the winter come to about 5,000feet.Sikka stay on the low ground in the woods.Roe stay in the same kind of environment and you might see them by the roadside. {Birds of Prey}are rare.The {Golden {Eagle }is the mascot of the Highlands of Scotland.They nest in cliffs or high branches in remote places.If you go to see any of these animals just watch them and please leave them alone.
